óŸOarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/columns.mdŸ@2a52578896ef1e047615d990ecb190ec5f26eab7c68625dadb750194e0932f67Ætitle: columnsë®Examples⁄ÚGet the columns from the record
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> { acronym:PWD, meaning:'Print Working Directory' } | columns
‚ï≠‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¨‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïÆ
‚îÇ 0 ‚îÇ acronym ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 1 ‚îÇ meaning ‚îÇ
‚ï∞‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¥‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïØ


```
Get the columns from the table
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[name,age,grade]; [bill,20,a]] | columns
‚ï≠‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¨‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïÆ
‚îÇ 0 ‚îÇ name  ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 1 ‚îÇ age   ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 2 ‚îÇ grade ‚îÇ
‚ï∞‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¥‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïØ


```
Get the first column from the table
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[name,age,grade]; [bill,20,a]] | columns | first


```
Get the second column from the table
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[name,age,grade]; [bill,20,a]] | columns | select 1


```
